data.description: Awesome 5 bedroom 4 and a half bath built in 2021! Walk into this bright and open home with 4 bedrooms and 2 and a half baths downstairs + game room, full bath and 1 bedroom upstairs. Open kitchen with island, pantry and tons of cabinet that extend all the way through the breakfast area. Living area with vaulted ceilings, wood floors, fireplace and more. Large formal dinning area currently being used as an awesome game room. Large primary bedroom with sitting area and a on suite primary bath. Primary bath has double sinks, separate shower and nice walk in closet. Upstairs game room with full bath, separate bedroom, and door to attic! This walk in room is great for storage or future expansion. Large backyard with privacy fence and covered back porch. All this +++ community club house, pool, playground and more. This is a must see!
